

Callbacks
=========

A callback function can be defined as a function passed into another function as a parameter.



function GeolocationCoordinates(name, callback) => {
    console.log('Hi', name)
    callback()
}

//callback function

function callMe(){
    console.log("I am a callback function")
}

//passing funciton as an arugment

great("vishnu", callMe)

//Hi vishnu
//I am a callback function
